{"tid":1070443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"年經:一人一個做過令父/母唔開心嘅事","createTime":"2019-03-20T16:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T07:02:33.000Z","uid":50384,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"999fcc8e7c2a2d463969b6cd5fa6739fdfabb8ce","tid":1070443,"uid":50384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"記得細個個時，<br />\n老竇朝頭早返工，夜晚上堂。<br />\n日日都好忙，假期就係屋企休息。<br />\n好少話帶我地岀去玩。<br />\n<br />\n咁有一年聖誕節，<br />\n可能老竇為咗氹我開心，<br />\n帶左我出去睇聖誕燈飾，<br />\n點知我就係中環聖誕樹下扭計喊話都冇嘢玩。<br />\n<br />\n我見到老竇呆左，<br />\n之後自言自語左一句&lsquo;我以為你會鍾意&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然嗰陣我好細個，但聽到之後個感覺好深刻。<br />\n第一次認真覺得自己做錯事，唔應該扭計。<br />\n宜家諗返都仲係好後悔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自此之後真係乖左好多,唔想再令老竇唔開心。<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999."},{"pid":"3942bc6440f94c0d86f97bb94b7971684a0a706e","tid":1070443,"uid":62822,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0500bf3a4b8720099edd845e903e425d848c786d","tid":1070443,"uid":50384,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95729a7a9aa1b45b104aad5af2a00f7ba1296b0","tid":1070443,"uid":165510,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"睇完個心好up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得中學有年反叛期 開始放學想同朋友出街遲返屋企唔聽電話<br />\n之後有次媽咪眼濕濕咁同我講其實去邊都唔緊要最緊要有交帶 唔好學壞<br />\n個下之後中學成日都好準時返屋企 去邊都同媽咪講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684b10c10437eb8e7da361e18be9aa41d8c9049a","tid":1070443,"uid":187076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"偷錢"},{"pid":"6c96c91c87c8e7b01acd79d8f38fdd5f5cf5132a","tid":1070443,"uid":203697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"反叛期亂發脾氣令老母唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bf2f4dd2ef98ecd59dcb11b0085729226a4866","tid":1070443,"uid":50384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4364c87624a8053f80607f471f9aea5c4871ae2a","tid":1070443,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"讀唔到博士<br />\n<br />\n都已經差唔多碩士畢業啦，走嚟同我講當年比心機啲嘅話而家應該係博士畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079699a6230302f339b141d4c3601df2c946d0cd","tid":1070443,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"考到正苦工但decline咗個offer<br />\n<br />\n媽咪嬲咗我半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa717447139ba450027c1d80c910488149ef9f5e","tid":1070443,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"為咗好少嘅事講大話呃老母<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣佢喊哂嘅樣但又不停鬧我大話精嘅樣一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從此發誓永遠唔講大話呃老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f44270b218190e527ab2771c3a7ca04c035873","tid":1070443,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"079699a6230302f339b141d4c3601df2c946d0cd","tid":1070443,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"考到正苦工但decline咗個offer<br />\n<br />\n媽咪嬲咗我半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"咁你抵嬲"},{"pid":"cb60abeb4246a834c8be74d69941aa73b48af55d","tid":1070443,"uid":85205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"以前細個個陣阿媽好想我入名校，四圍唔同嘅學校面試，結果面完試之後衰咗無一間收我，阿媽就鎖自己係房喊咗勁耐，仲發脾氣鬧咗我好耐<br />\n<br />\n過咗十幾年我宜家印象仲好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de1827cdc2b8cfeb7cfab0456f00db61e57e009","tid":1070443,"uid":229609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"生左我......<br />\n大家都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}